\p{\strong{For troubleshooting}: "To diagnose this issue, run [diagnostic command]. Based on the output, the solution will be [A] or [B]."}

\p{\strong{For analysis}: "To see [specific information], navigate to [location in mitmweb]. Look for [specific field/pattern]. This reveals [insight]."}
}

